---
import { Smile, Layers, ShieldCheck, Activity } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section id="servicios" class="py-24 bg-ice dark:bg-dark/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-dark dark:text-white">Especialidades con Sabor a Futuro</h2>
            <div class="w-20 h-1.5 bg-mint-500 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-mint-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-mint-50 dark:bg-mint-900/20 text-mint-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-mint-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                    <Smile class="w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-dark dark:text-white">Estética Menta</h3>
                <p class="text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Diseño de sonrisa con porcelana ultrafina para un look natural y vibrante.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-mint-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-mint-50 dark:bg-mint-900/20 text-mint-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-mint-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                    <Layers class="w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-dark dark:text-white">Ortodoncia Pro</h3>
                <p class="text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Alineadores invisibles de alta tecnología para corregir tu sonrisa cómodamente.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-mint-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-mint-50 dark:bg-mint-900/20 text-mint-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-mint-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                    <ShieldCheck class="w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-dark dark:text-white">Bio-Implantes</h3>
                <p class="text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Reposición de piezas con integración biológica perfecta y estética idéntica.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="group p-8 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all border border-transparent hover:border-mint-300 hover:-translate-y-2">
                <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-mint-50 dark:bg-mint-900/20 text-mint-500 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-mint-500 group-hover:text-white transition-all">
                    <Activity class="w-8 h-8" />
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3 text-dark dark:text-white">Higiene Fresh</h3>
                <p class="text-soft dark:text-mint-100/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Limpiezas por ultrasonido con acabado pulido y sabor a menta glaciar.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
